# Build artifacts
/sectors
/sectors.exe
/dist/

# Generated intermediate (produced by `go generate` from sectors-schema.json)
/sectors-schema.fixed.json

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.log

# Bulky mirror of upstream docs — exclude its contents, but keep our own
# endpoint→command map. Note: ignore /sectors-docs/* (contents), not the dir
# itself, so git still descends and the negation below can re-include the file.
/sectors-docs/*
!/sectors-docs/_ENDPOINT_INVENTORY.md